`public` is an **access modifier** that makes a class, method, or variable accessible from anywhere in your program.

## Usage Examples

### Public Class
```java
public class MyClass {
    // Accessible from any other class
}
```

### Public Method
```java
public class Calculator {
    public int add(int a, int b) {
        return a + b;  // Can be called from anywhere
    }
}
